Package de.fhb.sailboat.gui.missioncreator

This package provides all the needed tools do build and save missions via a graphical user interface.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
MissionCreatorInterface This class represents the graphical interface of the MissionCreator dialog.
MissionCreatorLogic This class holds the logic behind the workings of the MissionCreator dialog.
MissionInputAngleDialog This dialog enables easy input for angle tasks.
MissionInputPositionDialog This dialog enables easy input of positions (whether it be single GPS coord's or whole polygons).
MissionLoader This class enables the user to load Missions from files saved to disk.
MissionObject This class represents a mission (list of tasks) as a serializable object suited for saving/ loading.
MissionSaver This class enables the user to save missions (lists of tasks) to disk as files.
MissionTask This class serves but one purpose: Holding a Task in a serializable kind of form.
MissionTreeObject To be used as a userLoadObject within JTree.
 

Package de.fhb.sailboat.gui.missioncreator Description
